    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Casa Vieja is arguably one of Lester Hamlet's most acclaimed films, a modern-day adaptation of the play Casa Vieja by Abelardo Estorino in 1964. "
        }
      ]
